226%2FCNPB7PPKCBW773RDR6QQISFKUI%2F&h=a98091f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20170226/CNPB7PPKCBW773RDR6QQISFKUI/</a><br />\n========================<br />\n<br />\n只有臨近弱智嘅人先做到一隻聽話嘅狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48080f06ea10d4ae952581fa7f2109e1828532b4","tid":2391531,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"警甴"},{"pid":"e1adf1d6452b4351f42e35f062d8cd439c71dfd8","tid":2391531,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:51:04.000Z","msg":"挽回信心？咁集體自殺囉，民望會高翻！"},{"pid":"495f4f9525091b42590f1b7fc5b8967d2d227156","tid":2391531,"uid":305269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"教育局：橫掂都變香港市，不如就摺鬼咗口試佢啦，慢慢令學生覺得廣東話冇用仲好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2391657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2391657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c1a56208764616732c24e931492338697c9bd8ca","tid":2391531,"uid":21113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"做乜調查呀，人地話個仔大個要去做白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}